 <span data-ttu-id="4ac0e-321">ElementsWithOnlyAttributes.xml を作成します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4ac0e-321">Now create ElementsWithOnlyAttributes.xml:</span></span>  
  
